The Keiser Report  No. 210
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 15 November 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy discuss the Good, The Bad and the Schwing Schwing of making companies scared by putting risk back onto their balance sheet. They also discuss clients getting smoked through massive ploys in the commodity markets. 

In the second half of the show, Max Keiser interviews Mike Maloney of GoldSilver.com about the latest in the precious metals market and about a $15 trillion Dow.
